// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Static program tile data for the Bureau index page.
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
//
// Status values:
//   "live"     – program is shipping + monitoring real targets
//   "alpha"    – code lives in repo, accepts internal traffic only
//   "soon"     – committed in the plan, not yet started
//   "research" – in IDEAS.md, scope still firming
//
// At launch only Dragnet will be `live`. The others stay transparent
// about where they sit so the index is a credibility signal rather
// than vaporware.
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

